    "translation":{"eng":"It is His nature to distribute mercy to those souls who are utterly destitute [having no wealth other than Kṛṣṇa and service to Him], as well as to those who hanker for material possessions. His incomparable pastimes have thrown this foolish person named Rādhā-mohana into confusion."}}
